Emma gathered 2/3 of the total number she was allowed to take, which is 2/3 * 40 = 80/3 = 26.67 chicks.
To reach the total number she was allowed to take, Emma needs to collect 40 - 26.67 = 13.33 more chicks.
Since Emma can't take a fraction of a chick, she needs to collect 14 more chicks to reach the total number she was allowed to take home.
#### 14
The answer is: 14
